plot: The changing destinies of the Librarians.

Flynn returns with something that he says will restore the main library. He says thank you to Jenkins for providing him with the info that help him find it. But Jenkins says he didn't send him anything. That's when they all collapse and Dulaque shows up and reveals he was the one who sent Flynn the info. He then enters a portal, Eve and Flynn follow him and discover he's trying to tamper with the Loom of Fate. When he does it. Eve finds herself in alternate realities wherein Flynn never became the Librarian and Jacob, Cassandra and Ezekiel are Librarians.—rcs0411@yahoo.com
